          "type": "text",
          "text": " function is a scalar function in Microsoft SQL Server. Scalar functions return a single value, which can be used in SQL queries wherever expressions are allowed. This function is designed to provide a description for a given meter read reason code, which is typically used in utility billing systems to explain why a meter reading was recorded in a particular way."
